<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Congratulations</title>

  <!-- Modern clean font -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Khand:wght@500&family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4f8, #dfe6e9);
    }

    .wrapperAlert {
      width: 500px;
      max-width: 90%;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      background: #fff;
      animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .topHalf {
      position: relative;
      padding: 50px 20px;
      color: white;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b894, #55efc4);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .topHalf svg {
      fill: white;
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .topHalf h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-shadow: 0 3px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .bg-bubbles {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      z-index: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .bg-bubbles li {
      position: absolute;
      list-style: none;
      display: block;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      bottom: -160px;
      animation: square 20s infinite linear;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .bg-bubbles li:nth-child(1) { left: 10%; }
    .bg-bubbles li:nth-child(2) { left: 20%; width: 60px; height: 60px; animation-delay: 2s; }
    .bg-bubbles li:nth-child(3) { left: 25%; animation-delay: 4s; }
    .bg-bubbles li:nth-child(4) { left: 40%; width: 50px; height: 50px; animation-duration: 25s; }
    .bg-bubbles li:nth-child(5) { left: 70%; }
    .bg-bubbles li:nth-child(6) { left: 80%; width: 100px; height: 100px; animation-delay: 3s; }
    .bg-bubbles li:nth-child(7) { left: 32%; width: 160px; height: 160px; animation-delay: 7s; }
    .bg-bubbles li:nth-child(8) { left: 55%; width: 20px; height: 20px; animation-delay: 15s; animation-duration: 40s; }
    .bg-bubbles li:nth-child(9) { left: 25%; width: 10px; height: 10px; animation-delay: 2s; animation-duration: 40s; }
    .bg-bubbles li:nth-child(10) { left: 90%; width: 160px; height: 160px; animation-delay: 11s; }

    @keyframes square {
      0% { transform: translateY(0); }
      100% { transform: translateY(-600px) rotate(720deg); }
    }

    .bottomHalf {
      padding: 30px 25px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .bottomHalf p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #2d3436;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    button {
      background-color: #00b894;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #55efc4;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    button:active {
      transform: scale(0.97);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="wrapperAlert">
    <div class="topHalf">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 512 512" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
        <path d="M504 256c0 136.967-111.033 248-248 248S8 392.967 8 256 119.033 8 256 8s248 111.033 248 248zM227.314 387.314l184-184c6.248-6.248 6.248-16.379 0-22.627l-22.627-22.627c-6.248-6.249-16.379-6.249-22.628 0L216 308.118l-70.059-70.059c-6.248-6.248-16.379-6.248-22.628 0l-22.627 22.627c-6.248 6.248-6.248 16.379 0 22.627l104 104c6.249 6.249 16.379 6.249 22.628.001z"/>
      </svg>
      <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
      <ul class="bg-bubbles">
        <li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li>
        <li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bottomHalf">
      <p>Well done! You actually update your details successfully .</p>
      <button id="alertMO">Continue</button>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
